projectDesc.p: This dictionary was created by Andrew Attard and Jan Joachimsen using the original dictionary at http://www.aboutmalta.com/language/engmal.htm
The aim was to convert the dictionary in HTML format into a format for the use in META-SHARE and compliant to the standards of TEI.
This file is built using the FreeDict Dictionary TEI XML Template V0.1

change.item: V1.0: Converted the entries from the basic HTML-based dictionary. Still needs updating to the spelling with the special characters of the official orthography. Also the phonemic transcriptions should be in IPA or at least in SAMPA.
